desc: Cobblestone paths intersect beneath a weathered fountain. Lanterns hang from iron poles, flickering against the fading dusk. Prayer flags flutter gently overhead. A sense of history permeates the stones.
Broad stairs climb toward a marble archway. Devotees murmur hymns as they ascend. A sense of history permeates the stones. Vendors shout about today's wares.
